<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OCReal - Forgot Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #007bff;
    }

    p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    strong {
      color: #007bff;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>OCReal - Forgot Password</h1>
    <p>Hello {{fullname}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password. If you didn't make this request, you can ignore this email.</p>
    <p>If you did request a password reset, please use the following verification code:</p>
    <p>
      <strong>{{verificationCode}}</strong>
    </p>
    <p>This code will expire in 10 minutes for security reasons.</p>
    <footer>
      <p>Thank you for using OCReal!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>OCReal Team</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
